    <description><![CDATA[
# Ferrous Forge

**The Type-Safe Rust Development Standards Enforcer**

Ferrous Forge is a system-wide Rust development standards enforcer that automatically applies professional-grade coding standards to your Rust projects.

## Features

- **Rust Version Management** — Check and recommend Rust version updates
- **Edition Management** — Enforce Rust Edition 2024 compliance
- **Safety Pipeline** — Pre-commit and pre-push validation hooks
- **Standards Enforcement** — Clippy, formatting, security audits
- **Zero Configuration** — Works immediately after installation

## Quick Start

```powershell
# Install via Chocolatey
choco install ferrous-forge

# Initialize system-wide standards
ferrous-forge init

# Check your Rust version
ferrous-forge rust check
```

## Usage

Once installed, Ferrous Forge integrates with your cargo commands to enforce standards automatically.

For more information, visit: https://ferrous-forge.dev
]]></description>
